      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get the two sides, but doesn't calling things \"woke\" usually just feel like a way to dismiss actual progress? like, when people use it as an insult, isn't that basically just trying to shut down conversations about inequality? it feels like the \"critique\" is often just a way to avoid being held accountable.",
